high_descs: Turn around, head into the kitchen, take a left and go to the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is on the counter.
Turn to the left, go around to the other side of the counter to the black garbage can to the right of the door.
Cut the apple inside the garbage can with the knife.
Turn to the right, go to the end of the room, go to the left to the fridge.
Put the knife inside the fridge.
Turn around, go to the window, hang a right and go to the black garbage can to the right of the door.
Pick up a piece of apple from the garbage can.
Go around to the other side of the counter and head to the stove.
Put the apple on the white plate that is inside the cabinet that is above the left side of the stove.
Remove the plate containing the apple from the cabinet.
Turn around and head to the fridge that is on the left.
Put the plate containing the apple inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate containing apple in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the right, walk toward the refrigerator until passing the counter on the left, make a left and walk to the stove.
Pick up the knife from the counter to the left of the stove top.
Turn to the left, walk past the counter, turn to the right, and walk to the trash bin.
Cut the apple that is in the trash bin into thirds.
Turn to the right, walk towards the door, turning to the left before reaching it, walk to the refrigerator.
Open the door. Place the knife on the bottom shelf with the tomato.
Turn to the right and walk back to the trash bin.
Pick up a slice of the apple.
Turn right and walk back to the the stove top.
Open the left cabinet above the stove top and place the apple inside on the plate.
Remove the plate with the apple on top. Close the door.
Turn to the right and walk over to the refrigerator with the apple on the plate in hand.
Open the door. Place the apple on the plate on the top shelf. Close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place an apple slice on a plate into a refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the fridge then turn left and walk towards the stove, turn left and face the counter with the lettuce on it.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the end of the counter then turn right and walk towards the window then turn right and walk to the black trash can  to the right of the door.
Cut the apple in the trash can.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter then turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Put the knife inside the refrigerator.
Turn around and walk past the counter then turn right and walk to the black trash can.
Take an apple slice from the trash can.
Turn right and walk past the counter then turn left and walk towards the fridge, turn left and go to the stove.
Open the cupboard above the stove and put the apple on a plate in the cupboard.
Take the plate from inside the cupboard.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator on your right.
Put the plate inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the apple slice on the plate in the refrigerator.
